The year before I came,

236
00:14:28,325 --> 00:14:31,996
the Bulls had been eliminated
by Boston in the playoffs.

237
00:14:32,538 --> 00:14:33,956
<i>The ball game's over.</i>

238
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:36,250
<i>The series goes to Boston
in three straight.</i>

239
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:39,336
<i>The final score, 122-104, Celtics.</i>

240
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:41,630
The roster
