244
00:14:50,055 --> 00:14:52,725
He was a vicious rebounder,
brought a lot of toughness.

245
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:55,603
John Paxson was on that team,
Dave Corzine.

246
00:14:56,312 --> 00:14:58,814
