<i>All alone...</i>

259
00:15:32,139 --> 00:15:33,766
<i>Turns, off the glass.</i>

260
00:15:33,849 --> 00:15:36,018
<i>Forty-two points for Michael Jordan.</i>

261
00:15:36,727 --> 00:15:40,105
<i>Ten seconds on the shot clock,
Rory Sparrow working on it.</i>

262
00:15:40,189 --> 00:15:42,358
<i>Jordan, to the basket, scores.</i>

263
