268
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,835
I remember being on the plane,
going back to Chicago, I said,

269
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:05,631
"Wow. This guy is something
like I've never seen before."

270
00:16:05,714 --> 00:16:08,008
Doug and I, we're like this, you know.

271
00:16:08,592 --> 00:16:10,052
<i>He designed the offense</i>

272
00:16:10,886 --> 00:16:14,181
<i>to support the way I play the game
