273
00:16:14,264 --> 00:16:17,101
It's all right, Michael. It's all right.

274
00:16:17,184 --> 00:16:19,019
<i>I think he loved my competitiveness.</i>

275
00:16:19,103 --> 00:16:23,232
He understands that the greatest respect
you can give a great player

276
00:16:23,315 --> 00:16:25,275
is to coach him and coach him hard.

277
00:16:29,613 --> 00:16:31,156
<i>Michael's big thing was,</i>

278
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:33,367
"Stack the practice against me
