279
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:38,038
Doug always tried to maintain
a competitive advantage in practice.

280
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,712
I'd be with the starting five.

281
00:16:45,963 --> 00:16:47,256
Then next thing you know,

282
