331
00:20:25,766 --> 00:20:30,020
Back then, we played teams
six times in our division.

332
00:20:30,979 --> 00:20:33,982
They beat us six times, 6-0.

333
00:20:34,691 --> 00:20:36,860
So now in our mind,
we got nothing to lose.

334
00:20:38,528 --> 00:20:41,823
Bulls win the first game,
Cleveland wins the second in Cleveland.

335
00:20:41,907 --> 00:20:43,787
<i>Tied 1-1
with Cleveland's victory.</i>

336
00:20:43,825 --> 00:20:45,994
Back to Chicago,
Bulls win game three.

337
00:20:46,078 --> 00:20:48,372
<i>Chicago wins it, 101-94.</i>

338
00:20:48,956 --> 00:20:53,001
Game four, Jordan's got a free throw
