352
00:21:35,294 --> 00:21:37,504
So, Michael... Game's just about to start,

353
00:21:37,587 --> 00:21:41,258
Michael walks over to Lacy, and points
to him and says, "We took care of you."

354
00:21:41,341 --> 00:21:43,844
He looks at Kent and says,
"We took care of you."

355
00:21:43,927 --> 00:21:46,513
And he looks at me,
"And we take care of you today."

356
00:21:48,515 --> 00:21:50,892
<i>Mark Price and Ron Harper
in the backcourt</i>

357
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:53,020
<i>and we're underway. Cleveland has it.</i>

358
00:21:54,229 --> 00:21:56,481
We went back and forth
the whole time.

359
00:21:56,565 --> 00:21:59,359
<i>Jordan against Harper,
great turnaround.</i>

360
00:21:59,443 --> 00:22:00,986
It was a very tough game.

361
00:22:01,069 --> 00:22:02,654
<i>This is the playoffs,</i>

362
00:22:02,738 --> 00:22:06,199
<i>and here we have two great teams
right here, guys that lay it out.</i>

363
00:22:06,283 --> 00:22:07,326
It was a constant battle.

364
00:22:20,964 --> 00:22:23,604
<i>We have had drama
in the final minutes of the game.</i>

365
00:22:23,675 --> 00:22:26,136
<i>- Eleven seconds to go.
- In the middle...</i>

366
00:22:26,219 --> 00:22:27,471
<i>Jordan has it,</i>

367
00:22:27,554 --> 00:22:31,266
<i>and Jordan puts up a jumper and hits,
with six seconds to go.</i>

368
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:35,354
<i>Jordan hits the basket and now
has 42 points in the game,</i>

369
00:22:35,437 --> 00:22:38,065
<i>and the Cavaliers have called a timeout.</i>

370
00:22:38,648 --> 00:22:41,902
<i>Ehlo will inbound. He gets it in to Nance,
gets the ball back,</i>

371
00:22:41,985 --> 00:22:45,072
<i>drives to the hoop, lays it in
with three seconds to go.</i>

372
00:22:50,911 --> 00:22:53,246
<i>Here's our story,
here at Richfield Coliseum.</i>

373
00:22:53,330 --> 00:22:57,626
<i>One of these teams will advance.
