00:24:21,126 --> 00:24:23,837
I feel very vindicated from
when we started the playoff

398
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:26,131
with the dim look
that everybody was giving us...

399
00:24:26,214 --> 00:24:28,758
Even I asked you in the locker room,
I asked everybody,

400
00:24:28,842 --> 00:24:32,345
"What was the feeling back in Chicago?
Did they write us off yet?"

401
00:24:32,429 --> 00:24:34,181
You said, "Some of 'em
have written us off."

402
00:24:34,264 --> 00:24:35,849
I said, "Tell those guys to stay home."

403
00:24:36,433 --> 00:24:39,153
Somebody had written or said,
"The Bulls were gonna go home,

