407
00:24:48,278 --> 00:24:50,906
Whoever is not with us,
all you fuckers, go to hell.

408
00:24:50,989 --> 00:24:54,284
<i>Jordan beat them
at the buzzer with a jump shot.</i>

409
00:24:54,367 --> 00:24:56,828
It was so dramatic and it was typical

410
00:24:56,912 --> 00:25:00,248
of what we'd see Michael do
the rest of his career in big moments.

411
00:25:00,332 --> 00:25:05,003
That shot enabled the Bulls
to start growing

412
00:25:05,086 --> 00:25:07,714
and believing
that something special was on the horizon.

413
00:25:07,797 --> 00:25:10,926
We finally got over
the hump of losers' mentality.

414
00:25:11,009 --> 00:25:13,470
We were starting to become
a winning franchise,

415
00:25:14,054 --> 00:25:16,473
