434
00:26:20,787 --> 00:26:22,998
When we played the Pistons
in that series,

435
00:26:23,081 --> 00:26:26,751
it was...
it was arm-to-arm physical combat.

436
00:26:28,545 --> 00:26:30,964
But we never backed down. We fought them.

437
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:34,509
<i>The Bulls have won
the first game.</i>

438
00:26:34,593 --> 00:26:36,219
So we got game one.

439
00:26:36,303 --> 00:26:37,554
They won game two.

